Subject: ADI causing windows security auditing event 4662
Description:
When running ADI scan daily, does this job attempt to perform an operation on any AD object? or does it just read all of the objects?

It looks like ADI might be trying to perform an operation on an object. would like some assistance to investigate if possible.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Customer was receiving Windows Security Auditing 4662 Events and was looking for clarification as to why that would be

[Root Cause]
It wasn't the ADI job, but the Active Directory Weak Passwords job that was causing the alerts.

[Resolution]
Customer disabled the Weak Passwords job.
